/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T04:14:47.000Z","msg":"以前咸濕網吧都有...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，嫖客付五十元開機及每小時二百多元打機費，便有樣貌較普通的「網上情人」陪打機，任摸肉體。嫖客如打機超過一小時，可獲一百元嫖妓獎金，另可更換美貌性感女生或雙失少女陪伴打機，每五分鐘收費十七元。如女生及雙失少女提供額外的性服務，每項收費由一百至三百元不等。<br />\n<br />\n在色情網吧出賣色相及肉體的少女，工資被壓榨，她們每個小時只獲得三十至五十元鐘錢，有些無良的色情網吧，甚至沒有「拆帳」，少女只能透過為嫖客提供「特別性服務」取得收入，收費由少女與客人議價。"},{"pid":"20263fee521343a30b3759d0d741367e3b9ac4b0","tid":1980310,"uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"404081b1e18962962ccc01c64715a6df14cb6cac","tid":1980310,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57a0b5d88b339a9b6fb71db83c64eb2282109405","tid":1980310,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e5838a966b98a38e7962ac647a7f0f5fb83b0be","tid":1980310,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T04:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家班雞洗撚陪客 <br />\n學某隻肥豬賣相咪得囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T04:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T04:12:56.000Z","msg":"點睇最新陪打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T04:15:34.000Z","msg":"倍打機首先要把靚聲<br />\n屌，咪即係傾色情電話"},{"pid":"a6d8153de6208d49eae76cdcc1f564aace6c8e21","tid":1980310,"uid":192813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T04:15:50.000Z","msg":"個巴打好撚型"},{"pid":"f21b03f900606fda56ef262b51c14f73d29658ee","tid":1980310,"uid":64710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T04:20:12.000Z","msg":"隻g叫chris <br />\n係咪男人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5defb21f68e517dee29bdf4abd444e638e65b6","tid":1980310,"uid":128210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c9fa43735fbbf15a2bd1616b6239313e793db06","tid":1980310,"uid":1955